    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>酒类商店模拟器</strong>是一款关于经营发展自己商店的模拟游戏。您从一家贷款购买的小商店开始创业。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >起初并不容易—您需要亲自收银、进货、记账并维持卖场秩序。但通过努力工作和明智决策，您将能把小店发展成商品丰富、顾客满意的繁荣商店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采购商品，按您喜好布置卖场设备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.poster.avif?t=1770879223\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.webm?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.mp4?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生啤酒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验当调酒师的感觉。为顾客倒他们想要的啤酒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.poster.avif?t=1770879223\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.webm?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.mp4?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人员管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开始时您需要亲力亲为。但随着商店发展，您将需要雇用员工来协助经营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.poster.avif?t=1770879223\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.webm?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.mp4?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义装潢</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更改墙壁、天花板和地板的颜色。让您的商店独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.poster.avif?t=1770879223\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.webm?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.mp4?t=1770879223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
